flowchart TD
    A[Start PFAS CLI invocation] --> B[Resolve slab and PFAS inputs]
    B --> C[Step 1 sort water slab by oxygen z]
    C --> D[Step 2 xtb optimize slab]
    D --> E[Step 3 xtb optimize PFAS]
    E --> F[Step 4 KNF on optimized PFAS]
    F --> G{Orientation mode}

    G -->|perpendicular| H1[Place PFAS perpendicular]
    G -->|parallel| H2[Place PFAS parallel]
    G -->|dual| H1
    G -->|dual| H2

    H1 --> I1[xtb optimize interface perpendicular]
    H2 --> I2[xtb optimize interface parallel]

    I1 --> J1[Geometry analysis]
    I2 --> J2[Geometry analysis]

    J1 --> K1[KNF on interface]
    J2 --> K2[KNF on interface]

    K1 --> L[Compute energies and KNF deltas]
    K2 --> L
    L --> M[Pick preferred orientation by minimum Delta E ads]
    M --> N[Write summary json and summary txt]
    N --> O[End]
